502
00:48:30,240 --> 00:48:32,880
I'll find you.

503
00:48:35,920 --> 00:48:38,680
Lucy! We have to go right now.

504
00:48:44,600 --> 00:48:45,600
It's okay.

505
00:48:55,240 --> 00:48:56,720
