520
00:52:09,920 --> 00:52:10,960
Got them all out

521
00:52:11,920 --> 00:52:13,400
but he couldn't save himself.

522
00:52:14,440 --> 00:52:15,920
He's gone. I'm sorry.

523
00:52:18,080 --> 00:52:19,400
You're lying.

524
00:52:20,400 --> 00:52:23,080
- I wish I was.
